THIS REVOCATION FORM. HAVE IT ACKNOWLEDGED BEFORE A NOTARY PUBLIC OR
OTHER INDIVIDUAL AUTHORIZED UNDER LAW TO TAKE ACKNOWLEDGMENTS.
RECORD THE FORM IN THE LAND RECORDS OF EACH COUNTY WHERE THE
PROPERTY IS LOCATED. THE FORM MUST BE ACKNOWLEDGED AND RECORDED
BEFORE YOUR DEATH OR IT HAS NO EFFECT.
HOW DO I FIND THE “LEGAL DESCRIPTION” OF THE PROPERTY? THIS
INFORMATION MAY BE ON THE TRANSFER–ON–DEATH DEED. IT MAY ALSO BE
