TITLE OF OFFICE
STAMP
MY COMMISSION EXPIRES: ________
CERTIFICATION OF OCCUPANCY STATUS
SELECT ONE OF THE BELOW OPTIONS THAT CORRECTLY DESCRIBES THE
PROPERTY’S OCCUPANCY STATUS:
OPTION ONE:
____ NONE OF THE BENEFICIARIES INHERITING THE SUBJECT PROPERTY UNDER
THE DEED REFERENCED IN THIS NOTIFICATION LIVE AT THIS PROPERTY AS THEIR
PRINCIPAL RESIDENCE.
OR
OPTION TWO:
____ AT LEAST ONE OF THE BENEFICIARIES INHERITING THE SUBJECT PROPERTY
UNDER THE DEED REFERENCED IN THIS NOTIFICATION LIVES AT THIS PROPERTY AS
THEIR PRINCIPAL RESIDENCE.
IF YOU SELECTED OPTION TWO AND YOU ARE THE BENEFICIARY OCCUPYING THE
PROPERTY, PLEASE COMPLETE THE FOLLOWING:
I, ______________________ (PRINT NAME), DO HEREBY CERTIFY AND AFFIRM UNDER
THE PENALTIES OF PERJURY THAT I CURRENTLY LIVE AT AND WILL CONTINUE TO
LIVE AT THE ABOVE–REFERENCED PROPERTY, FOLLOWING THE RECORDING OF
THIS NOTIFICATION. I SHALL OCCUPY THE PROPERTY AS MY PRINCIPAL RESIDENCE
FOR AT LEAST 7 OF THE NEXT 12 MONTHS.
